org.wikidata.wdtk.wikibaseapi

Class WbGetEntitiesActionData

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.wikidata.wdtk.wikibaseapi.WbGetEntitiesActionData

  • public class WbGetEntitiesActionData
extends Object
    This class is a simple record that holds the properties of an wbgetentities action request. It is used internally by WikibaseDataFetcher to gather parameters for the request.
    Author:
    Michael Guenther
